Faktorial:

$$0! = 1$$

$$n! = n * (n-1)!$$

Contoh:

\begin{align*}
5! &= 5 * 4! \\
&= 5 * 4 * 3! \\
&= 5 * 4 * 3 * 2! \\
&= 5 * 4 * 3 * 2 * 1! \\
&= 5 * 4 * 3 * 2 * 1 * 0! \\
&= 5 * 4 * 3 * 2 * 1 * 1 \\
&= 120
\end{align*}

